17:02.329 --> 17:03.779
How did I forget this part?

17:03.813 --> 17:05.881
And when did we stop giving
children cigarettes?

17:05.915 --> 17:08.032
It's the liberal war
on Leap Day.

17:08.084 --> 17:11.287
It's time to go,
Mr. Donaghy.

17:11.320 --> 17:15.590
Welcome to Leap Day present.

17:15.625 --> 17:17.560
Okay, I'll change
me eye color,

17:17.594 --> 17:20.095
but it seem like
a waste of voodoo.

17:20.130 --> 17:23.682
Good night, Mr. Donaghy.

17:23.717 --> 17:25.233
