rhubarb there is.

18:09.479 --> 18:10.879
The one that's
as big as me, sir?

18:10.897 --> 18:12.714
That's the one.

18:12.732 --> 18:16.551
But first, you take Rebecca
Birdstein to the vet.

18:16.569 --> 18:17.853
What a Mitzvah.

18:17.887 --> 18:19.688
Merry Leap Day, sir.

18:19.722 --> 18:21.573
Merry Leap Day to us all!

18:23.026 --> 18:25.077
Liz, why don't you go and...

18:25.111 --> 18:26.495
Get you and Karolina
